ability Through AI Data<\/span><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Contextual Relevancy Aids Personalization<\/span><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">AI-Based Insight For Betterment Of Customer Activation<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>This article will take a studious look into how AI helped Nike&#8217;s customer experience strategy grow. We will also look at some of the most revolutionary Nike artificial intelligence applications that may become a norm in the near future.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"box-cta -bg -border -narrow lazy colors-inverted\"\n     data-bg=\"https:\/\/www.digitalsilk.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/Software-Development-655x230.jpg\">\n\n\t        <a href=\"https:\/\/www.digitalsilk.com\/development-services\/custom-software-development\" class=\"box-cta__wrap\">\n    \n        <div class=\"box-cta__text-wrap\">\n            <div class=\"l-heading-v3\">\n                <div class=\"c-heading -h2\">\n                    \n                                            <div class=\"c-heading__title\">Explore Digital Silk&#8217;s Custom Software Development Services<\/div>\n                                    <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"box-cta__icon\">\n            <svg class=\"icon icon-lib-icon-arrow-right-big \"  aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#lib-icon-arrow-right-big\"><\/use><\/svg>        <\/div>\n\n            <\/a>\n    \n<\/div>\n\n\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_45_1 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" area-label=\"ez-toc-toggle-icon-1\"><label for=\"item-63f324de35678\" aria-label=\"Table of Content\"><span style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;width: 3